snippet.title: Evercade Atari Collection 2 Cartridge Trailer
snippet.description:
Visit: http://evercade.co.uk/atari-collection-2-cartridge/

The Atari Collection 2 brings 20 more classic Atari 2600 and Atari 7800 games to the Evercade! The cartridge will be supplied in a stunning collectable retro style physical case with full colour manual!

Full games list: 

Asteroids (7800)
Yars' Revenge (2600)
Millipede (2600)
Basketbrawl (7800)
Centipede (7800)
Solaris (2600)
Sprintmaster (2600)
Submarine Commander (2600)
Haunted House (2600)
Planet Smashers (7800)
Bowling (2600)
Desert Falcon (7800)
Radar Lock (2600)
Human Canonball (2600)
Street Racer (2600)
Air Sea Battle (2600)
Realsports Tennis (2600)
Dark Chambers (2600)
Wizard (2600)
Demons to Diamonds (2600)
